sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant User as User / Pipeline
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as ServingRuntime Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>(PredictorReconciler)
    participant MM as ModelMesh (mm)<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd Cluster<br/>2379/TCP gRPC
    participant Puller as Puller Container<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Runtime as ML Runtime Container<br/>Unix Socket gRPC
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>8008/TCP HTTP
    participant Client as Inference Client

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: Model Deployment (Predictor/InferenceService Creation)
        User->>K8sAPI: Create Predictor/InferenceService<br/>HTTPS · Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (CRD change)
        Controller->>MM: gRPC SetVModel<br/>8033/TCP · Optional TLS/mTLS
        MM->>etcd: Store model state<br/>2379/TCP · Optional TLS
        MM->>Puller: Fetch model artifacts<br/>8086/TCP gRPC (pod-local)
        Puller->>Storage: Download model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS · TLS 1.2+<br/>Backend-specific credentials
        Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
        Puller-->>MM: Model loaded<br/>Unix socket / 8085/TCP gRPC
    end

    rect rgb(230, 255, 230)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Inference (gRPC)
        Client->>MM: gRPC inference request<br/>8033/TCP · Optional TLS/mTLS<br/>Optional mTLS client certs
        MM->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>Unix socket · gRPC
        Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
        MM-->>Client: gRPC response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 3: Model Inference (REST via OAuth)
        Client->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS POST<br/>8443/TCP · TLS<br/>OpenShift OAuth token
        OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: HTTP forward<br/>8008/TCP (localhost)
        RESTProxy->>MM: gRPC call<br/>8033/TCP · Optional TLS
        MM->>Runtime: Forward to runtime<br/>Unix socket · gRPC
        Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
        MM-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
        OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 230, 255)
        Note over etcd,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Model State Event Streaming
        etcd->>Controller: Watch event (model state change)<br/>2379/TCP gRPC · Optional TLS
        Note over Controller: ModelMeshEventStream →<br/>PredictorReconciler<br/>(in-process Go channel)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Predictor/InferenceService status<br/>443/TCP HTTPS · ServiceAccount token
    end
